{"tid":963088,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【咁着數？】抽中大獎放有薪年假1年 真相係......","createTime":"2018-12-31T10:51:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T02:50:22.000Z","uid":39464,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"74a079583c0ff68e1e163f5d372e875e07a0c061","tid":963088,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T10:51:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181231/large/1546246469_1287.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181231%2Flarge%2F1546246469_1287.jpg&h=327cc71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上海一間公司日前舉辦年會，一名「幸運」女員工抽中「超級大獎」，其獲獎照在網上被瘋傳，見她拿着大大的獎品紙板，上寫道「上海辦公室年會特等獎帶薪年假一年」，令許多網民羨慕不已，但原來這獎品是內有玄機。<br />\n因為這個特等獎雖寫着「帶薪年假一年」，但原來是有「使用期限」，有眼尖網民在照片右下角發現，帶薪年假有效期只到2018年12月31日，但頒獎日期是2018年12月28日，換言之，得獎女員工只得29、30及31共有3天有薪年假，而且這3天本身就是中國元旦假期，女員工其實甚麼也沒得到。<br />\n網民們紛紛留言：「放心吧，馬上就過年了」、「愚人節嗎？」、「有效期笑死我了」、「哪間公司？老闆很幽默啊」、「最終解釋權歸本公司所有」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181231/59090355\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181231%2F59090355&d=cTAjkEOo76T5poMGkCYoaWMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=c106bc9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181231%2F59090355&h=673fff0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181231/59090355</a>"},{"pid":"4a92feba4cc97e2bee0417f20fbf5524c6c58ba0","tid":963088,"uid":66324,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T10:55:11.000Z","msg":"大陸老細度縮程度超越港豬了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a75e8e922cef115b126def2ddc218fc3e213732","tid":963088,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T11:36:11.000Z","msg":"So funny"},{"pid":"4878f66dd056570f3574d86dbfda905b82fee79b","tid":96308